public class ProductDIP
extends Product
The Product DIP class defines a product for the Dissemination Information Package.

Java class for Product_DIP complex type.

     <extension base="{http://pds.nasa.gov/pds4/pds/v1}Product">

    • getInformationPackageComponents

      public List<InformationPackageComponent> getInformationPackageComponents()
      Gets the value of the informationPackageComponents property.

      This accessor method returns a reference to the live list, not a snapshot. Therefore any modification you make to the returned list will be present inside the JAXB object. This is why there is not a set method for the informationPackageComponents property.

      For example, to add a new item, do as follows: 

          getInformationPackageComponents().add(newItem);

      Objects of the following type(s) are allowed in the list InformationPackageComponent
